description: KGB Gourmet Food Truck is definitely the way to go if you’re looking for some quality cuisine on the streets of Omaha. Their menu features all your favorite comfort classics, such as Kebobs, Gyros, and Brats (of course, it’s KGB!),  made with authentic Mediterranean ingredients, for a marvelously tasty experience. Come out to KGB and try their grilled brats, sausages, and dogs, and pile on the yummy toppings, or their selection of big juicy burgers, fresh & savory gyros, salads, nachos, or other scrumptious eats.For all this and much more deliciousness, you simply must visit KGB Gourmet Food Truck ASAP!
name: KGB Gourmet Food Truck
